code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     Map<String, String> body = new HashMap<>().     body.put("Hello", "World").     exchange.getIn().setBody(body). }

@Test public void testFirstSampleJolt() throws Exception {     Exchange exchange = template.request("direct://start", new Processor() {          @Override         public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {             Map<String, String> body = new HashMap<>().             body.put("Hello", "World").             exchange.getIn().setBody(body).         }     }).     assertEquals(3, exchange.getOut().getBody(Map.class).size()).     assertEquals("aa", exchange.getOut().getBody(Map.class).get("a")).     assertEquals("bb", exchange.getOut().getBody(Map.class).get("b")).     assertEquals("World", exchange.getOut().getBody(Map.class).get("Hello")). }

@Override protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          public void configure() {             from("direct://start").to("jolt:org/apache/camel/component/jolt/defaultr.json?transformDsl=Defaultr").         }     }. }
